flowchart LR
  Browser[User Browser\n(JS frontend)]
  Browser -->|GET /| StaticHTML[Static HTML + JS (templates/index_fastapi.html)]
  Browser -->|POST /predict| API[FastAPI (uvicorn)\n/api.py]
  Browser -->|GET /config| API
  API -->|loads| Model[Model Pipeline\nmodels/xgboost_pipeline.pkl (joblib)]
  API -->|compute| SHAP[SHAP Explainer\nTreeExplainer -> PNG: static/shap_<id>.png]
  API -->|calls| LLM[Local LLM Server\nspawned subprocess or external URL from .env]
  LLM -->|HTTP response| API
  API -->|serves| StaticFiles[/static/*]
  API -->|reads/writes| Env[.env (LLM paths, args)]
  Model -->|trained on| Dataset[dataset/healthcare-dataset-stroke-data.csv]
  subgraph ServerProcess[Server Host]
    API
    Model
    SHAP
    LLM
    StaticFiles[/static]
    Env
  end
  API -->|logs/metrics| Monitoring[(Logging / Metrics)]
  Browser -->|view| Results[Prediction + Readable Text + SHAP Image + Suggestions]
  Results -->|optionally| Download[(Export PPT/PNG/Report)]
  click Model href "models/xgboost_pipeline.pkl" "Model file"

